{"ts": "2026-06-08T03:53:14.366992+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here is a summary of the project setup and day-to-day development commands, gathered from `package.json`, `README.md`, and supporting config files in the repository.\n\n---\n\n## Project Overview\n\nThis is a **Vue.js 3 + Vite** starter template with Pinia, Vue Router, Bootstrap 5, SCSS, Vitest, ESLint, Prettier, and Husky/lint-staged. The package manager is **pnpm** (v10.20.0 as specified).\n\n---\n\n## Setup (first-time)\n\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n\n- Node version: **v24** (from `.nvmrc`). If using `nvm`, run `nvm use` first.\n- `preinstall` hook enforces pnpm via `npx only-allow pnpm`.\n- `prepare` hook runs `husky` to set up Git hooks.\n\n---\n\n## Day-to-Day Commands\n\n### Development Server\n\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n# or simply:\npnpm dev\n```\n\nStarts the Vite dev server with hot-reload.\n\n### Build (production)\n\n```bash\npnpm run build\n# or:\npnpm build\n```\n\nCompiles and minifies for production.\n\n### Preview Production Build\n\n```bash\npnpm run preview          # preview last build\npnpm run build-preview    # build + preview in one step\n```\n\n### Unit Tests\n\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit            # run tests (Vitest, watch mode by default)\npnpm run test:unit-coverage   # single run with coverage report\n```\n\nTest config is embedded in `vite.config.js` under the `test` key (Vitest with jsdom environment, global setup files in `tests/`).\n\n### Lint\n\n```bash\npnpm run lint                # check all .vue, .ts, .js files\npnpm run lint-fix            # auto-fix lint issues\n```\n\nESLint uses `@kouts/eslint-config` (see `eslint.config.js`).\n\n### Formatting (Prettier)\n\nNot a dedicated script in `package.json`, but Prettier is configured (`prettier.config.js`) and can be invoked directly:\n\n```bash\nnpx prettier --check .       # check formatting\nnpx prettier --write .       # fix formatting\n```\n\n### Pre-commit Hooks\n\n- **Husky** (`prepare` script, `.husky/`) manages Git hooks.\n- **lint-staged** (`lint-staged.config.js`) runs `npm run lint-fix` on staged `*.vue` and `*.js` files before commit.\n- **commitlint** (`commitlint.config.js`) enforces conventional commit messages.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 595, "prompt_tokens": 5398, "total_tokens": 5993, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 24, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 5120}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 5120, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 278}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "521381c1-5208-4d05-85d1-60cf0c822968", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea55c-cdc9-7b63-9fcd-6fb95af3c79b-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5398, "output_tokens": 595, "total_tokens": 5993, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 5120}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 24}}}}]}}}
